            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-63d70b7c-fee7-49f2-a12f-db0e9853e1a6" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
