                Mr. George Griffiths
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-97c8808a-43bc-4b4c-9da7-2c26c34d4c58" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
