<p class="">Obviously I cannot announce what the amount is. This is a policy which is in the hands of the authorities of Eire and it would be improper for me to make a guess at what they may be likely to spend in carrying out the policy which they have announced.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
